🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept two numbers from user and display division of two numbers use raise to display divided by zero exception messages.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE divide(a INT, b INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
BEGIN
    IF b = 0 THEN
        RAISE EXCEPTION 'Division by zero not allowed';
    END IF;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Division = %', a / b;
END;
$$;


